ck-OSS/bedrock-wiki&#34;&gt;github.com/Bedrock-OSS/bedrock-wiki&lt;/a&gt; - 许可说明：以原仓库或原站点公开许可声明为准。 ...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/guide/loot-table/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 13:41:18 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/guide/loot-table/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/bedrock-wiki/guide/loot-table.png" type="image/png" length="10639" /> </item> </channel> </rss>